This Privacy Policy elucidates the data collection, utilization, and security measures employed by Dynasty of Wealth, an application (""App""). By utilizing this App, you acknowledge and consent to the methods of data collection and use as detailed below.
Personal identifiable information is solely procured upon voluntary submission, such as name or email, predominantly during user-initiated support inquiries or feedback provisions.
The App autonomously gathers non-identifiable data, including device specifications and user interaction patterns, aimed at enhancing user experience and App functionality.
The acquired information serves the following objectives:
- Occasional communication via email regarding updates or offers, with an opt-out provision for user discretion.
Compliance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) is maintained for users within the European Economic Area (EEA).
Residents of California hold rights under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), encompassing data access, deletion, and disclosure queries.

The App is not intended for users under 13 years of age. No data collection from minors is knowingly entertained. If inadvertently obtained, contact us at contact@dynasty61.com for swift rectification.
Stringent measures are in place to ensure the security of user information. However, absolute security in online data transmission or storage cannot be guaranteed.
For inquiries or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, or to exercise GDPR, CCPA, or related rights, please reach out to us at contact@dynasty61.com.
Alterations or updates to this Privacy Policy may occur periodically. All modifications take immediate effect upon publication. Regular review of this page is advised to stay informed of any changes.
This Privacy Policy exclusively pertains to data collected by the Dynasty of Wealth Android App. External websites or services linked within the App operate under their respective privacy protocols."
